title: Best of Interviews ( City Girls & Kanye West First Interview)
itunes:title: Best of Interviews ( City Girls & Kanye West First Interview)
description:
Today on the show we flashed back to when both City Girls called in and spoke about what certain songs on their new album meant, not dating a broke dude, the industry grind and so much more. Also, since the show made it to 10 years, we had to flash back to when Kanye West made his first debut interview as Kanye Kardashian as Charlamagne would like to say. Also, we flashed back to when Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" for his comments about Gabrial Union accusations on "America's Got Talent". Check it out now
